        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks CD for two letters and his portrait.</p> 
<p>CD’s book [<hi rend="italic">Orchids</hi>] opened up <hi rend="italic">terra incognita</hi> for him.</p> 
            <p>His work on S. African butterflies continues.</p>
            <p>Reports on a moth that punctures peach skins.</p>
            <p>Interesting that thoughtful naturalists are forced to admit mutability of species.</p> 
<p>Some notes on <hi rend="italic">Oxalis</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
